eupscaler.com" style="color:#3b82f6;text-decoration-line:none;text-decoration:underline" target="_blank">Contact us</a></p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;color:#64748b;margin:4px 0;margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0"><a href="https://myimageupscaler.com/api/campaigns/unsubscribe?token=test-unsubscribe-token-123" style="color:#3b82f6;text-decoration-line:none;text-decoration:underline" target="_blank">Unsubscribe from marketing emails</a></p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;color:#64748b;margin:4px 0;margin-top:4px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-left:0">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> <!-- -->MyImageUpscaler<!-- -->. All rights reserved.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></body></html><!--/$-->"`;

